            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> </strong>roughly</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1651675626081-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1651675626081-x400.jpg",
