            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>spaghetti</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the spaghetti for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain the <strong>cooked spaghetti</strong> and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
